What you need to know:

Oman's Sultan Qaboos, who transformed the former Arabian Peninsula backwater into a modern state and the Gulf's discreet mediator, dies aged 79.One of the last stars of Hollywood's golden age, Kirk Douglas, dies at his home in Beverly Hills aged 103.Egypt's former president Hosni Mubarak, who was swept from power by the Arab Spring in 2010, dies in a military hospital aged 91.